text: Þas bocas haueð Salomon preost, þæt is þe codspel traht & þe martyrliua & þe æglisce saltere & þe cranc & ðe tropere, & Wulfmer cild þeatteleuaui& pistelari & ðe imnere & ðe <capitelari> & þe spelboc, & Sigar preost þe leceboc & Blakehad boc, & Æilmer ðe grete sater & ðe litle tropere forbeande & ðe donatum, XV bocas.
Ealfric, Æilwine, Godric, & Bealdewuine abbot, & Freoden, & Ðuregisel.
